<style>
  :root {
    --radius: 26px;
  }

  .about {
    background: var(--c-bg);
    padding: 48px 24px 40px;
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-family: "Jost", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Itim", sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5em;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--c-primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-grid {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 340px 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Left column */
  .profile {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    justify-items: start;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 22px;
    border: 4px solid var(--c-primary);
    background: #fff;
  }

  .profile-actions {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hl {
    color: var(--c-primary);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 2px solid var(--c-primary);
    color: var(--c-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  }
  .btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 3px solid var(--c-primary);
    padding: 18px 18px 16px;
  }

  .card--tall {
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: var(--c-primary);
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .subbox {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    padding: 12px 12px 8px;
  }

  .subbox h4 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: var(--c-primary);
  }

  .subbox ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
  }

  .likes {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 26px auto 0;
    max-width: 900px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .likes > p {
    color: var(--c-textlight);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .card--tall {
      grid-row: auto;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="about" id="about">
  <h2>About me</h2>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <aside class="profile">
      <img
        class="profile-photo"
        src="portrait.JPG"
        alt="Portrait photo"
      />
      <!-- <div class="profile-actions">
        <a class="btn" href="resume-en.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resume (EN)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="resume-de.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resume (DE)</a>
      </div> -->
    </aside>

    <div class="cards">
      <article class="card card--tall">
        <h3 class="hl">Game Developer</h3>
        <p>
          I'm specialized in Unity Game Development. I can iterate game systems,
          write documentation and integrate functions.
        </p>

        <div class="subbox">
          <h4>Using</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>- Unreal Engine 5 (Blueprints)</li>
            <li>- Unity (C#)</li>
            <li>- Versioning (git)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card card--tall">
        <h3>Generalist</h3>
        <p>
          Working solo on several projects allowed me to learn a handfull of
          tools useful for developing games and help around in many creative
          areas.
        </p>

        <div class="subbox">
          <h4>Using</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>
              - Adobe suite: After effects, Premiere, Photoshop, Illustrator,
            </li>
            <li>- Subtance Tools: Painter, Designer</li>
            <li>- Blender (3,4,5)</li>
            <li>- Reaper and FMOD</li>
            <li>- Aseprite</li>
            <li>- Google and Microsoft suite</li>
            <li>- Teamtools like: Trello, Miro, Teams, Slack</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>
      <div class="likes"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
